graph LR
  APIGW[API Gateway]
  subgraph Services
    AUTH[auth-service]
    USER[user-service]
    ACADEMIC[academic-service]
    PRED[prediction-service]
    ANALYTICS[analytics-service]
  end
  subgraph Databases
    PG[(PostgreSQL)]
    MONGO[(MongoDB)]
    REDIS[(Redis)]
  end
  APIGW -->|/api/v1/auth| AUTH
  APIGW -->|/api/v1/users| USER
  APIGW -->|/api/v1/academic| ACADEMIC
  APIGW -->|/api/v1/prediction| PRED
  APIGW -->|/api/v1/analytics| ANALYTICS

  USER --> PG
  ACADEMIC --> PG
  ANALYTICS --> PG

  PRED --> MONGO

  AUTH --> REDIS
  ANALYTICS --> REDIS
